  "text": "Cell viability was determined using the 3-(4,5-dimethylthiazol-2-yl)-2,5-diphenyltetrazolium assay [CITATION_1] . For this, fibroblasts (3 x 10 4 cells/well) were treated and after 1, 2 or 3 days of treatment, 3-(4,5-dimethylthiazol-2-yl)-2,5-diphenyltetrazolium solution (Sigma-Aldrich) was added [CITATION_2] . The results were expressed as the percentage of the control (medium-only) group.",
